ISLAMABAD, Jan 05 (APP): Caretaker Minister for Communications, Maritime Affairs and Railways Shahid Ashraf Tarar on Friday called on Caretaker Prime Minister Anwaar-ul-Haq Kakar.
In the meeting, the matters pertaining to the relevant ministries were discussed, a PM Office press release said.
